---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Concrete Removal"
  description={`Concrete removal services in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC: driveways, patios, retaining walls and flatwork. Free estimates from Nesbitt's Plumbing: ${site.phone}.`}
  heroTitle="Remove Old Concrete From Your Property"
  heroSubtitle="Ask about Nesbitt's Plumbing's concrete removal services in the Asheville & Hendersonville, NC areas."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-20.jpg"
  listHeading="Types of concrete features we remove"
  listItems={[
    'A spalled driveway so that you can install a new, more durable driveway',
    'An unused patio so that you can clear the way for a new landscape feature',
    'A cracked retaining wall so that you can replace it with a stone or brick wall',
  ]}
  listNote="Concerned about the cost? Don't be. Contact us today to get a free estimate for concrete removal services."
  ctaHeading="Ready to Clear Out That Old Concrete?"
>
  <p>
    Asheville, NC is known for its historic homes and beautiful landscapes. Unfortunately, older
    properties have old concrete that's no longer up to par. If you're ready to rid your property
    of worn-out concrete features, call Nesbitt's Plumbing right away.
  </p>
  <p>
    We're known throughout the Asheville, NC area for our top-notch concrete removal services.
    With {site.yearsInBusiness} years of experience, we have what it takes to get rid of concrete
    features of all types and sizes, including flatwork. You can trust us to do the job right.
  </p>
  <p>
    Call <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    for your free estimate.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
